{"tid":165080,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 (有片）- 水牛城雞翼 (Buffalo Wings) 脆皮版","createTime":"2017-03-21T06:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T05:38:11.000Z","uid":30742,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e78bcadad7217fa85e5cb5f7bc173d6d018b5cfc","tid":165080,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JtuJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJtuJQ.jpg&h=e2ea9393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HnP_7GsWk-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHnP_7GsWk-M&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=04b6e8e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HnP_7GsWk-M</a><br />\n<br />\nBuffalo Wings其實有好多唔同既食譜，有炸有焗有光波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我炸同焗都有做，兩款都ok既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但重口味既我最鍾意就梗係炸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲係要有脆皮包住果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢次我用左以前韓國炸雞既方法去處理<br />\n個皮會厚dddddd<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就算上埋汁都keep到脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身諗住食兩隻架ja&hellip;但最後都係忍唔住&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水牛城雞翼 (Buffalo Wings) 脆皮版: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/03/buffalo-wings.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F03%2Fbuffalo-wings.html&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fb648311\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/03/buffalo-wings.html</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=dd5370a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5e948ad7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a82b3fe1\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"83c93e65b2367c448d355fb2005470cffdf50379","tid":165080,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"射左"},{"pid":"d5feb77566fe192c0c03d8933d8bb39ffa315967","tid":165080,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:05:58.000Z","msg":"老娘B<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11500ac9e3239cec8b729865b95b109be808097e","tid":165080,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘B<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做咩比人偷名咁大鑊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccd6689c0e341560fb5214e58a8e2e60b7e448a","tid":165080,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hk