.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaa2f954bcafa23463a0dce1cbd796268e241c2","tid":165080,"uid":5762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:04:07.000Z","msg":"本來餓餓哋<br />\n睇埋呢個po仲餓<br />\n老娘你要負責任呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab18bda574734f0de4740c4c1f548b3cf6b3ac11","tid":165080,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前姐夫都整過一次<br />\n不過無落辣椒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點埋個芝士醬勁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下次落埋辣椒仔～你會覺得呢個世界真係好美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢用左另一隻整buffalo wings嘅辣醬去代替左<br />\n好撚辣但真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1875ab40bd6c39841dafe19b17819761d9b789","tid":165080,"uid":71373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:39:44.000Z","msg":"依個方法改焗，唔用炸得唔得<br />\n唔想用咁多油<img src=\"/assets/faces